    "In contrast, the compositional questions need chart recognition followed by calculation and reasoning, heavily relying on MLLM's reasoning ability.",
    "This confirms the validity of the hypothesis.To gain deeper insights into the underlying reasons for the issue, we examine the responses generated by MLLMs equipped with CoT.",
